export type Options = $ReadOnly<{|
  date?: ?(Date | number),
  minDate?: ?(Date | number),
  maxDate?: ?(Date | number),
  mode?: ?('calendar' | 'spinner' | 'default'),
|}>;

export type DatePickerOpenAction =
  | {|
      action: 'dateSetAction',
      year: number,
      month: number,
      day: number,
    |}
  | {|
      action: 'dismissedAction',
      year: void,
      month: void,
      day: void,
    |};
